page.title: 03The Shillito Family's Day
page.content: { 13:6:1985}I myself, M.Shillito and family went to a National trust house in{Cornwall,}it had a copy of the{DOMESDAY BOOK}which we are renewing.We went to the beach next day and saw a male & female{ {Kestrel}(a bird of prey) the male was hunting & the female was sitting on her nest. My family has six people in it,me,my mum, dad, Phill(my brother),Ed (my brother),Jon (my brother). The common family has 2 children and 2 adults. We usually eat potatoes:chips,baked beans, eggs,meat,cheese. My age is 10 my brothers ages are Ed 12, Phill 19, and Jon 21.
